---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base title="Clarity. â€” Why Clarity.?">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">
    <!-- Heading sits visually above the box -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Why Clarity.</h1>

    <!-- Why Clarity Explainer -->
    <section
      class="mt-[1rem] bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 opacity-90">
        You don't need more noise. You need someone who gets it. <br />
        The context. The constraints. The pressure to decide and move.<br /><br
        />

        That's where Clarity. comes in.<br /><br />
         We work in your world, not adjacent.<br
        /> We use your language, not ours.<br /> We bring experience, not opinion.<br
        /> We give you tangible next steps you can act on immediately.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Clarity. grid -->
    <section class="mt-20 text-left">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Real Understanding.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            Your language. Your constraints. Your goals. <br />
            Faster traction. Less translation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Confident Decisions.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            We combine proven frameworks with lived experience. <br />Clear.
            Justified. Actionable recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Faster Progress.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            You'll leave each engagement with tangible outputs:<br /> Priorities.
            Blockers. Next steps. Immediate progress.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">Zero Overhead.</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            Our approach is designed to extract insight quickly. <br />You get
            value without adding more to your plate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation Arrows -->
    <section class="my-32 flex justify-center items-center gap-16">
      <!-- Left Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/our-support-plans"
        aria-label="Previous page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Right Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/what-is-insight-as-a-service"
        aria-label="Next page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section
      id="final-cta"
      class="mt-20 bg-gray-900 text-white py-12 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Feel ready?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
        That's why Clarity exists.<br /> We give you information and insight so you
        can make great decisions. <br /><br />No fluff. No spam. Just Clarity.<br
        /><br />
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
        >Join the Waitlist</a
      >
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
